<title>mạly swạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-
 mạly swạk yạ sydy ḥyạty rḍạk yạ sydy
 ạ̉nt mtkly mṭmỷn nfsy
 2- ḥlw mạ ạ̉sẖhạk yạ sydy nfsy lạ tslạk yạ sydy
 tfrḥ qlby ạ̉nrt ly drby
